article_text: Parnell said he was creating a Medicaid reform group to study the system and report back in a year. He also directed Streur to report back on the health-care needs of uninsured people who fall below the federal poverty line. He said he expects that information in hand in time to make amended budget requests to the Legislature in 2014. Critics were skeptical any improvements would materialize soon.
